dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.resource.res.log.trans.tp.TPAspectCompoundResourceDetails
dataStructure.description:
This class is a concrete class that defines the semantics of the TPsInResourcePort aggregation. For example, it will describe characteristics and behavior of the TerminationPoints that make up this particular ResourcePort in terms of dependencies and how a TerminationPoint interacts with other TerminationPoints.This aggregation defines the set of TerminationPoints that make up this particular RsourcePort.

This association class is optional
dataStructure.label: TPAspectCompoundResourceDetails
